movie_name: Nosferatu - Ein Film wie ein Vampir
short_description: Nosferatu, approaching his hundredth birthday, travels to sites used in the film, meets with experts, tells us about his "fathers" (the men who created the film), and reflects on changes in European society and culture since 1922.
